
wine
- red wine: cabernet, merlot, pinot noir
- white wine: chardonnay, pinot grigio
beer
- lager/pilsner: light, crisp, refreshing
- pale ales/IPAs: bitter, hoppy beers
- wheat beers/hefeweizens: wheaty flavor
- dark (stout, porter): coffee-flavor
hard alcohol:
- whiskey, scotch (whiskey from scotland)
- rum
- tequila
- vodka
